Tools and Technologies used:
Java 8
Maven
TestNG
SLF4J
GitHUb
Rest Assured framework for api automation
IntelliJ IDEA IDE



How to Run All tests  at a time in MAC:
-> go to inside project
-> open mac terminal
-> enter mvn test


How to Run one testcase  at a time in MAC:
-> go to inside project
 src->test->java->testcases
-> right click on Individual testcase, run as testng test




API examples
getweather details

method: get
url : http://restapi.demoqa.com/utilities/weather/city/Hyderabad


create  customer details

method : post
url : http://restapi.demoqa.com/customer/register

Header:
Name: Content-Type
Value:application/json

payload:

 {
   "FirstName" : "mahesh",
   "LastName" : "patnam",
   "UserName" : "maheshpatnam",
   "Password" : "Voiceworks02",
   "Email"  : "mahesh.patnam221@gmail.com"
 }


expected code :201


